---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<section class="relative text-white overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <img src={`${base}images/uchimado/photo-5.jpg`} alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover" fetchpriority="high" />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gray-900/80"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 md:py-32">
    <div class="text-center bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl px-6 py-10 md:px-12 md:py-14">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent-500 text-gray-900 font-bold px-5 py-2 rounded-full mb-6 animate-fade-in-up text-sm md:text-base">
        2026年から非住宅も新たに対象
      </div>

      <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm md:text-base mb-4 animate-fade-in-up">神戸の窓ガラス専門店 MADOA（株式会社三喜）</p>

      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6 animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-200">
        店舗・クリニック・事務所の<br />
        窓リフォームに<span class="text-accent-400">最大1,000万円</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-200 mb-4 animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-200">
        先進的窓リノベ2026 -- 非住宅の窓断熱リフォームが補助金対象に
      </p>
      <p class="text-base text-accent-300 font-bold mb-8 animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-200">
        補助金の申請手続きはすべてMADOAにおまかせ
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-300">
        <a
          href="#contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent-500 hover:bg-accent-600 text-gray-900 font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-full text-lg transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-105"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M2.003 5.884L10 9.882l7.997-3.998A2 2 0 0016 4H4a2 2 0 00-1.997 1.884z" />
            <path d="M18 8.118l-8 4-8-4V14a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8.118z" />
          </svg>
          無料で補助金対象か確認する
        </a>
        <a
          href="tel:078-597-2722"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-full text-lg transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-105"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M2 3a1 1 0 011-1h2.153a1 1 0 01.986.836l.74 4.435a1 1 0 01-.54 1.06l-1.548.773a11.037 11.037 0 006.105 6.105l.774-1.548a1 1 0 011.059-.54l4.435.74a1 1 0 01.836.986V17a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2C7.82 18 2 12.18 2 5V3z" />
          </svg>
          078-597-2722
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 mt-4 animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-400">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 bg-white/15 backdrop-blur-sm text-white text-sm font-semibold py-1.5 px-4 rounded-full border border-white/20">見積無料</span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 bg-white/15 backdrop-blur-sm text-white text-sm font-semibold py-1.5 px-4 rounded-full border border-white/20">出張費無料</span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 bg-white/15 backdrop-blur-sm text-white text-sm font-semibold py-1.5 px-4 rounded-full border border-white/20">補助金申請代行</span>
      </div>

      <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mt-4 animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-400">
        受付時間: 8:30〜17:30（土日祝休み）
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 80" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-full">
      <path d="M0 80L60 73.3C120 66.7 240 53.3 360 46.7C480 40 600 40 720 46.7C840 53.3 960 66.7 1080 70C1200 73.3 1320 66.7 1380 63.3L1440 60V80H1380C1320 80 1200 80 1080 80C960 80 840 80 720 80C600 80 480 80 360 80C240 80 120 80 60 80H0Z" fill="white"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>
